description: Ohio, you hungry? Well, we have some GOODE news for you! Hatfield’s GOODE GRUB is roaming your streets and boy, there’s no denying how dang good this grub is. The Cleveland crowds are completely crazy for this Southern Comfort cuisine, and who can blame them when they’re biting into beautifully crafted burgers and BBQ slathered in Chef Ken’s Blue Ribbon Sauce? Their Pulled Pork Sandwiches and Quesadillas are positively pleasing, and the Bacon Mac & Cheese will keep you coming back. It’s like their Uncle Tadpole’s Catfish Stew was made just for you, and just wait till you take a peek at their whole menu!Take a pit stop at this truck and hit the spot with this GREAT Goode Grub.
name: Hatfield's Goode Grub
